    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What's new in the Steam version?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can paddle Banana and Watermelon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;In the depths of difficulty, your paddle becomes your anchor of hope.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A physics driven boat paddling game. Paddle that boat to the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realtime world physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited fail attempts allowed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10/10 heavy motivation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to play:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are two ways to paddle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Click your Left mouse button gently or fastest you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Press Z key on your keyboard continuously until that broke.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Warning:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please protect your fingers while playing.</p>",
